      • verifyEventArchiveSupport

        public static void verifyEventArchiveSupport(String instance)
                                      throws BadRequestException
        Checks if events are supported for the specified instance. This will succeed in two cases:
        1. EventRecorder is currently enabled
        2. EventRecorder has been enabled in the past, but may not be any longer
        Throws:
        BadRequestException
